caption: The image is a purple and white graphic featuring a single eye with a light bulb in the center. The text "It's Better To Light A Candle Than To Curse The Darkness" is displayed above the eye, emphasizing the importance of positivity and illumination in life. The image is likely meant to inspire viewers to focus on the good and bright aspects of life, rather than dwelling on negativity and darkness.
